					<li>Not causing damage to the physical (hardware) and logical (software) systems of Smart AI Hacks.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Consent</h2>
				<p>
					Your continued use of our website will be regarded as acceptance of our practices around privacy and personal information. If you have any questions about how we handle user data and personal information, feel free to contact us.
				</p>
			</section>

			<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8">
